  mutterVeryDissatisfied: The aliens are conferring with each other...
  mutterDissatisfied: The aliens exchange glances...
  mutterNeutral: The aliens observe quietly...
  mutterSatisfied: The aliens murmur amongst themselves...
  mutterVerySatisfied: The aliens react with visible excitement!
  narrationVeryDissatisfied: They seem very displeased...
  narrationDissatisfied: They do not appear to like it.
